title: Cast of ‘The Real Housewives of Atlanta,’ Then & Now (PHOTOS)
text:
NEXT Advertisement 
The Real Housewives of Atlanta has been giving us life for the past nine seasons, but many fans have no clue who these successful women truly were before the reality show. 
Sure, we know Kenya Moore is a former beauty queen and Kandi Burruss was a member of 90’s R&B group Xscape, but it’s a different experience actually seeing our favorite housewives outside of the realm of the show. 
Check out throwback pics of the RHOA cast above! 
Real Housewives of Atlanta airs Sundays at 8 p.m. ET on Bravo.
